text: Wuhan University () is a university in Wuhan, China. It started teaching in 1893. The buildings and the cherry blossom in the university are very beautiful and well known. People think it is one of the most beautiful universities in China. Ten most beautiful campuses in China, No. 1 is Wuhan University. ==References== Category:Colleges and universities in the People's Republic of China Category:1893 establishments Category:1890s establishments in Asia Category:19th-century establishments in China Category:Wuhan
